{"nodes":[{"pos":[12,49],"content":"Compiler Error C2432 | Microsoft Docs","needQuote":false,"needEscape":true,"nodes":[{"content":"Compiler Error C2432 | Microsoft Docs","pos":[0,37]}]},{"content":"Compiler Error C2432","pos":[597,617]},{"content":"illegal reference to 16-bit data in 'identifier'","pos":[618,666]},{"content":"A 16-bit register is used as an index or base register.","pos":[673,728]},{"content":"The compiler does not support referencing 16-bit data.","pos":[729,783]},{"content":"16-bit registers cannot be used as index or base registers when compiling for 32-bit code.","pos":[784,874]},{"content":"The following sample generates C2432:","pos":[881,918]}],"content":"---\ntitle: \"Compiler Error C2432 | Microsoft Docs\"\nms.custom: \"\"\nms.date: \"11/04/2016\"\nms.reviewer: \"\"\nms.suite: \"\"\nms.technology: \n  - \"devlang-cpp\"\nms.tgt_pltfrm: \"\"\nms.topic: \"error-reference\"\nf1_keywords: \n  - \"C2432\"\ndev_langs: \n  - \"C++\"\nhelpviewer_keywords: \n  - \"C2432\"\nms.assetid: 0e3326e8-cab1-45a5-b48d-61edd33793e8\ncaps.latest.revision: 7\nauthor: \"corob-msft\"\nms.author: \"corob\"\nmanager: \"ghogen\"\ntranslation.priority.ht: \n  - \"cs-cz\"\n  - \"de-de\"\n  - \"es-es\"\n  - \"fr-fr\"\n  - \"it-it\"\n  - \"ja-jp\"\n  - \"ko-kr\"\n  - \"pl-pl\"\n  - \"pt-br\"\n  - \"ru-ru\"\n  - \"tr-tr\"\n  - \"zh-cn\"\n  - \"zh-tw\"\n---\n# Compiler Error C2432\nillegal reference to 16-bit data in 'identifier'  \n  \n A 16-bit register is used as an index or base register. The compiler does not support referencing 16-bit data. 16-bit registers cannot be used as index or base registers when compiling for 32-bit code.  \n  \n The following sample generates C2432:  \n  \n```  \n// C2432.cpp  \n// processor: x86  \nint main() {  \n   _asm mov eax, DWORD PTR [bx]   // C2432  \n}  \n```"}